Package: idar
Title: Identification Analysis and Structural Causal Model Estimation in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person(given="Diogo", family="Ferrari", email="diogoferrari@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2454-0776")))
Description: End-to-end estimation of structural causal models (SCM), from the specification of the data generating process (DGP) using a directed acyclic graph (DAGs) to identification analysis, selection of adjustment variables (selection on observables), estimation of causal effects, and estimation results summary and plotting.
